{"tid":903414,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"朱克伯格要求FB高層只用Android手機","createTime":"2018-11-15T13:55:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-17T02:09:20.000Z","uid":28765,"like":11,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"f4b9036019bb74b67ed662debf84059cd51e28e1","tid":903414,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T13:55:29.000Z","msg":"全球Android系統用戶愈來愈多，Facebook創辦人朱克伯格（Mark Zuckerberg）向其管理團隊下達命令，稱只能用Android手機。有分析推測，Facebook是次舉措是因早前蘋果（Apple）行政總裁庫克（Tim Cook）接受美國媒體MSNBC訪問時，曾批評Facebook提供「販賣用戶的個人生活」服務有關，同時暗示Facebook以用戶私隱來賺錢。<br />\n<br />\n據外國科技網站《The Verge》報導，今年3月庫克接受訪問時，被問及如果他是Facebook創辦人，會如何應對英國政治顧問公司劍橋分析（Cambridge Analytica）從Facebook非法獲取用戶資料的醜聞。庫克當時回應指，「我不會面對這種情況」。<br />\n<br />\n朱克伯格隨後接受傳媒訪問時反駁庫克，批評他言論「極度未經深思熟慮（extremely glib）」，並強調「我們都不應該患上斯德哥爾摩症候群（Stockholm syndrome），讓一些千方百計希望在你身上賺錢的公司，說服你相信他們確實關心你。這個想法在我聽來是荒謬的。」<br />\n<br />\n有外媒分析指，雖然尚未知是次指令與庫克言論有否關係，但Facebook的做法仍算合理，因Android的操作系統在世界各地相當普及，如果開發人員少用Android手機的話，在開發應用程式時可能會遇上盲點。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://wealth.hket.com/article/2209112/朱克伯格要求FB高層只用Android手機\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwealth.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2209112%2F%E6%9C%B1%E5%85%8B%E4%BC%AF%E6%A0%BC%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82FB%E9%AB%98%E5%B1%A4%E5%8F%AA%E7%94%A8Android%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F&d=ZM%2FYmqnHOnhqe5jVT8WB9f755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=2eb95d4b\" target=\"_blank\">https://wealth.hket.com/article/2209112/朱克伯格要求FB高層只用Android手機</a>"},{"pid":"a97353287c2ae96298fe35f9b49d0ed877dda281","tid":903414,"uid":12628,"like":30,"dislike":4,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T14:48:02.000Z","msg":"豬閪份人好方丈"},{"pid":"d282480ed1ef58c4afb5995717c30327a3d9156f","tid":903414,"uid":839,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T14:49:33.000Z","msg":"話得你唔啱咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4358fbefcdff9c9bef3225021e19e871a5f8da3e","tid":903414,"uid":13663,"like":22,"dislike":2,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T14:50:51.000Z","msg":"指定用華為啦 豬閪"},{"pid":"12ec1ca3fc562e4a69f1ccd88cd4fbbc4fe2a165","tid":903414,"uid":35070,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T15:09:29.000Z","msg":"其實Android版Facebook好撚頓胎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc7cde56d04ac15c2c0d49513a7344e570e58f70","tid":903414,"uid":109383,"like":4,"dislike":9,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T15:38:57.000Z","msg":"並強調「我們都不應該患上斯德哥爾摩症候群（Stockholm syndrome），讓一些千方百計希望在你身上賺錢的公司，說服你相信他們確實關心你。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n並強調「我們都不應該患上斯德哥爾摩症候群（Stockholm syndrome），讓一些千方百計希望在你身上拎到data的公司，說服你相信他們確實關心你的私穩。"},{"pid":"ad6367a47a750d600e0ee6c85157b93c9f6c6426","tid":903414,"uid":168366,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T15:40:28.000Z","msg":"Gay cook 表示 wfc <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38bccd0cc7c3b1fbe6df90cc0ab146861d11bee4","tid":903414,"uid":26602,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"12ec1ca3fc562e4a69f1ccd88cd4fbbc4fe2a165","tid":903414,"uid":35070,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T15:09:29.000Z","msg":"其實Android版Facebook好撚頓胎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T05:25:01.000Z","msg":"ios 定 android個facebook app都係一舊食位嘅垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f5f39d91b805d95e3b74b7c4ffe90316a09aee4","tid":903414,"uid":14548,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T05:35:58.000Z","msg":"App store落埋架佢囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"706a6be8ab6b16cb5802e7546cc2b743997f3283","tid":903414,"uid":5846,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"dc7cde56d04ac15c2c0d49513a7344e570e58f70","tid":9